skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily dinner
des:
Finding something to cook every day is a hard task. With this skill, Alexa will recommend a dinner to you every day. You will never confuse what you will cook

Getting Started:
- Open "Daily Dinner Recommendation" skill page on Alexa app or alexa.amazon.com
- Click Enable Skill button
- Now, you can use skill with example phrases

To get recommendation dinner just say:
- Alexa, ask daily dinner, what can I cook today
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
